data.text:
Hes a smallish car thats comfy for me to drive but theres surprising a lot of leg room. 

The dashboard is rly neat and does some cool stuff. 

Ok thats it for now im sure ill found out more cool stuff

Theres a sunroof!!!!!!!

The old owners also tinted the windows which idk how i feel about but it looks cool

The brakes are v sensitive which rocks cause my old cars were terrible.

Hes push to start and the door has a touch sensor so i dont have to use my keys ever.

He has rly good ac, and thank god cause ive been two summers without it and ive been dying. 

The middle screen is a touch screen and its rly easy to play music. 

The old owners got a solar panel put in on the top for the battery.

Theres a usb port and two plug in areas.
@S0YLEM THANK YOU IM SO HAPPY WITH HIM!!
